commit.message:
par-labl.adb, [...]: Fix copyright notices.

	* par-labl.adb, restrict.adb, s-osinte-hpux-dce.ads, sem_ch11.adb,
	exp_pakd.adb, s-filofl.ads, par-endh.adb, exp_intr.adb, sem_cat.adb,

From-SVN: r160982
